title: DJ 2Sugars - The Best of UKG (www.myspace.com/dj2sugars)
description:
The Latest CD from the Award Winning UK Garage DJ \"DJ 2Sugars\".

A mixture of the Best New & Old UKG Mixed live @ Alex\&#039;s Bar Magaluf.

DJ 2 Sugars first started DJ\&#039;ing at Top Night Club Alex\&#039;s last year and has since gained a reputation as one of the best Garage DJ\&#039;s in the Business.

DJ 2 Sugars has just been signed to the world famous Twice as Nice label and will be appearing at a club near you soon.
